# ✅ 4️⃣ Prevent State Update (Fallback Pattern)

If cancellation is **not supported** (older APIs):

```jsx
useEffect(() => {
  let isActive = true;

  fetch("/api/data")
    .then(res => res.json())
    .then(data => {
      if (isActive) setData(data);
    });

  return () => {
    isActive = false;
  };
}, []);
```

✅ Prevents stale updates  
❌ Request still runs in background

***

# ✅ 5️⃣ Cancel Previous Requests on Button Click

```js
let controller;

function fetchData() {
  if (controller) controller.abort();

  controller = new AbortController();

  fetch("/api/data", { signal: controller.signal });
}
```

✅ Useful outside React effects

